T02TD2916E:315a-1: badzra bi d'a ra na ka la sha bi dhi:/
T02TD2916E:315a-3: rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa'i bum pa'i cho ga / rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2916E:315a-4: yid du 'ong ba'i sa yi char //
T02TD2916E:315a-5: kun du spyod pa gtsang ldan pas //
T02TD2916E:315a-6: gser ram dngul lam khams gzhan gyis //
T02TD2916E:315a-7: bum pa mtshan nyid bzang ldan pa //
T02TD2916E:315a-8: legs bkrus dkar po'i rdzas kyis byugs //
T02TD2916E:315a-9: dris bdug ras kyis mgul pa dkris //
T02TD2916E:315a-10: me tog srad bus mdzes byas par //
T02TD2916E:315a-11: rin chen rma med tsandan dri //
T02TD2916E:315a-12: rgyun 'bab chu yis legs bkang ba //
T02TD2916E:315a-13: bzang po'i shing gis kha brgyan te //
T02TD2916E:315a-14: sa dang lci bar bsres pa yi //
T02TD2916E:315a-16: d'ur ba'i stan la yang dag gzhag / dri zhim chu yis bkang ba'i snod //
T02TD2916E:315a-17: rdo rje me tog phreng bar ldan //
T02TD2916E:315a-18: rang lha'i bsam gtan la gzhol bas //
T02TD2916E:315a-19: stong pa'i sngags kyis rnam sbyangs te //
T02TD2916E:315a-20: bh'um las rin chen gzhal yas khang /
T02TD2916E:315a-21: bam byung 'o ma'i rgya mtshor ldan //
T02TD2916E:315a-22: pam pad aa las zla dkyil 'khor //
T02TD2916E:315a-23: der gnas h'um yig spro bsdu las //
T02TD2916E:315a-24: khro bo khro mo'i 'khor lo bskyed //
T02TD2916E:315a-25: ye shes spyan drangs mchod pa dang //
T02TD2916E:315a-26: bstod dang gnyis su med par bya //
T02TD2916E:315a-27: dbang bskur slar yang mchod bstod nas //
T02TD2916E:315a-28: rang snying sngags kyi phreng bkod de //
T02TD2916E:315a-29: bzlas dang bum par spro bya bar //
T02TD2916E:315a-30: lan grangs nyi shu rtsa gcig gam //
T02TD2916E:315a-31: yang na brgya rtsa brgyad la sogs //
T02TD2916E:315a-32: ji srid mngon par 'dod pa'i mthar //
T02TD2916E:315a-33: mchod bstod 'dod don gsol ba dang //
T02TD2916E:315a-34: lha rnams ye shes bdud rtsi yis //
T02TD2916E:315a-35: rab bkrus gtsang mar gyur pa dang //
T02TD2916E:315a-36: nad med bgegs rnams 'joms pa dang //
T02TD2916E:315a-37: dpal du byed cing bkra shis dang //
T02TD2916E:315b-0: phun @315b sum tshogs min 'joms par byed //
T02TD2916E:315b-1: rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa'i bum pa'i cho ga rdzogs so//
